      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Mar 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-03-10/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Breach Tally: Hacking Incidents Still on the Rise&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So far in 2017, hacking incidents continue to affect the largest number of individuals impacted by major health data breaches. Meanwhile, incidents &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.govinfosecurity.com/breach-tally-hacking-incidents-still-on-rise-a-9762&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.govinfosecurity.com/breach-tally-hacking-incidents-still-on-rise-a-9762&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;New law will force some (but not all) organisations to reveal data breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the case of attacks leading to data breaches, they could then report to a governmental department that would non-selectively provide live website &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://theconversation.com/new-law-will-force-some-but-not-all-organisations-to-reveal-data-breaches-73971&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://theconversation.com/new-law-will-force-some-but-not-all-organisations-to-reveal-data-breaches-73971&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Are you hacker proof or an old hack? Avoiding the next Ashley Madison&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First, not all data breaches are reportable data breaches. Those that are reportable must be reported to the Office of the Australian Information &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.moneymanagement.com.au/features/are-you-hacker-proof-or-old-hack-avoiding-next-ashley-madison&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.moneymanagement.com.au/features/are-you-hacker-proof-or-old-hack-avoiding-next-ashley-madison&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Shareholder sues Yahoo directors for delaying disclosure of massive data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;KTVU San Francisco It contends they should forfeit their profits from alleged insider trading in stocks they sold when they knew about the data breaches but most of the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.ktvu.com/news/240688880-story&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.ktvu.com/news/240688880-story&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;10 Important Cyber Security Tips For Small Business Owners&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On any given day, they can fell to the hacking, malware, ransomware and data breaches due to their cheap and dated protection. But with the few &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.informationsecuritybuzz.com/articles/10-important-cyber-security-tips-small-business-owners/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.informationsecuritybuzz.com/articles/10-important-cyber-security-tips-small-business-owners/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Tips for Evaluating Next Gen Endpoint Security Solutions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Traditional preventative measures alone offer insufficient endpoint protection  causing an influx of vendors offering NGES. While the market is &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://webinar.darkreading.com/2862?keycode=sbx&amp;cid=smartbox_techweb_webcast_8.500000719&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://webinar.darkreading.com/2862?keycode=sbx&amp;cid=smartbox_techweb_webcast_8.500000719&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Fortune 1000 Companies Two Times More Prone To Data Breaches, Says Report&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The top 1000 companies listed by Fortune magazine may be more vulnerable to security breaches, when compared to peers which do not make the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.themarshalltown.com/fortune-1000-companies-two-times-more-prone-to-data-breaches-says-report/26836&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.themarshalltown.com/fortune-1000-companies-two-times-more-prone-to-data-breaches-says-report/26836&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;CEO from Massena-based SeaComm Federal Credit Union travels to Washington&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;North Country Now Data breaches cost hundreds of thousands of dollars to credit unions like ours. There is nonexistent merchant data security standards which make &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://northcountrynow.com/business/ceo-massena-based-seacomm-federal-credit-union-travels-washington-dc-hike-hill-conference&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://northcountrynow.com/business/ceo-massena-based-seacomm-federal-credit-union-travels-washington-dc-hike-hill-conference&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Security: Businesses Biggest Fear From Data Breaches is Reputation Loss&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lost customer personal data. That&amp;rsquo;s bad, but what businesses fear most about data breaches is the black mark on the reputation of the business.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://formtek.com/blog/security-businesses-biggest-fear-from-data-breaches-is-reputation-loss/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://formtek.com/blog/security-businesses-biggest-fear-from-data-breaches-is-reputation-loss/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;New law will force some (but not all) organisations to reveal data breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Changes to the way some organisations must reveal a data breach on personal information. Credit: Rawpixel com. We live in an era of big data stored &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://phys.org/news/2017-03-law-organisations-reveal-breaches.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://phys.org/news/2017-03-law-organisations-reveal-breaches.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

